          "html": "<div dir=\"ltr\"><p>Dear Customer Care Team,</p>\n<p>I recently purchased a product (Order Number: [Your Order Number]) and need immediate assistance. There appears to be an issue that requires urgent attention: [briefly describe the issue, e.g., damaged product, incorrect item, missing parts].</p>\n<p><strong>Details:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Order Number: [Your Order Number]</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Purchase Date: [Date]</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Issue Description: [Explain clearly what went wrong]</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Photos/Attachments: [Attach if available]</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Please advise on the next steps to resolve this issue promptly, including options for a replacement, refund, or return. I would greatly appreciate a response as soon as possible to avoid further delays.</p>\n<p>Thank you for your immediate attention to this matter</p></div>\n",
          "text": "Dear Customer Care Team,\n\nI recently purchased a product (Order Number: [Your Order Number]) and need\nimmediate assistance. There appears to be an issue that requires urgent\nattention: [briefly describe the issue, e.g., damaged product, incorrect\nitem, missing parts].\n\n*Details:*\n\n   -\n\n   Order Number: [Your Order Number]\n   -\n\n   Purchase Date: [Date]\n   -\n\n   Issue Description: [Explain clearly what went wrong]\n   -\n\n   Photos/Attachments: [Attach if available]\n\nPlease advise on the next steps to resolve this issue promptly, including\noptions for a replacement, refund, or return. I would greatly appreciate a\nresponse as soon as possible to avoid further delays.\n\nThank you for your immediate attention to this matter\n",
          "textAsHtml": "<p>Dear Customer Care Team,</p><p>I recently purchased a product (Order Number: [Your Order Number]) and need<br/>immediate assistance. There appears to be an issue that requires urgent<br/>attention: [briefly describe the issue, e.g., damaged product, incorrect<br/>item, missing parts].</p><p>*Details:*</p><p>   -</p><p>   Order Number: [Your Order Number]<br/>   -</p><p>   Purchase Date: [Date]<br/>   -</p><p>   Issue Description: [Explain clearly what went wrong]<br/>   -</p><p>   Photos/Attachments: [Attach if available]</p><p>Please advise on the next steps to resolve this issue promptly, including<br/>options for a replacement, refund, or return. I would greatly appreciate a<br/>response as soon as possible to avoid further delays.</p><p>Thank you for your immediate attention to this matter</p>",
